notes: The data set consists of human poverty index value  with varaiables such as percentage of people not expected to survive to age 40, adult illiteracy rate, percentage without safe water, percentage of children under age five who are malnourished and deprivation in economic provisioning by disticts for 2011. The data is extracted from Nepal Human Developement Report (2014) by UNDP (http://www.npc.gov.np/new/uploadedFiles/allFiles/NHDR_Report_2014.pdf).
